      <link>https://www.npr.org/2023/12/20/1220726464/states-are-trashing-troves-of-masks-and-protective-gear-as-costly-stockpiles-exp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着明年分配联邦 COVID-19 现金的最后期限临近，各州必须决定在大流行期间的恐慌性购买后投资多少资金来维持仓库和供应库存。]]></description>
